{"tid":1538500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由七月開始逃犯條例已經一定唔會通過，由頭到尾都唔係重點","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:22:57.000Z","uid":164590,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1628c8b0a112862cc0885b70d17d1dc190949c64","tid":1538500,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"好可惜你而家撤回已經冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家係要雙普選<br />\n同埋黑警填命</span>"},{"pid":"ad642ee7ad473f033c59a9d8483fdbbd5dd3aa12","tid":1538500,"uid":164590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱毛孟靜都講咗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啲傷者係送去瑪嘉烈醫院並唔係廣華醫院<br />\n如果有咩事黑警都要付出相同嘅代價</span>"},{"pid":"77d69d8fefb4eee48cd3de7674a8362508978ab9","tid":1538500,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d72d1d8ff44053183541e4d8e2e2b1f54c8c882","tid":1538500,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kybLqX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkybLqX5.jpg&h=ae2d5f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"2461ae1bb997f680016e9257903c12b12970c6d4","tid":1538500,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人填命屌你老母"},{"pid":"b3f4c93d129e3e4cd1eb5b6a4431375a866df77c","tid":1538500,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a889SFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa889SFe.jpg&h=3fb438bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd9f3f0eaf4799c8151954a8c8233e36494cb0f3","tid":1538500,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"一定會血債血償"},{"pid":"d46a5b498239ab4013849e3313bbb15e3e6d736b","tid":1538500,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br